Class RawOrFFTParams

java.lang.Object
Localiser.controls.RawOrFFTParams
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, RawOrFFTParamsInterface, ManagedParameters
public class RawOrFFTParams extends Object implements Serializable, Cloneable, RawOrFFTParamsInterface, ManagedParameters
Parameters to use when a data source can be either raw or fft data. invalid input: '<'br for use with RawOrFFTPane dialog component. Should be embedded in more complex dialog components.

dg50
